c: 11
v: 12
t: "Saka pamwe iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) unosiya chidimbu chezvawakazarurirwa, uye chipfuva chako chinomanikana nazvo nokuda kwekuti vanoti: “Nei hupfumi husina kutumirwa kwaari, kana ngirozi kuuya naye?” Asi uri muyambiri chete. Uye Allah ndiWakil (Mumiriri kana Muchengetedzi) wezvinhu zvose"